title: Approach S20: Style on the wrist meets confidence on the tee.
description: Check out the new Approach S20 from Garmin. It’s a stylish timepiece, a daily activity tracker, and an awesome golf watch that can help improve your game. It comes preloaded with more than 40,000 courses from around the world – plus automatic map updates, AutoShot round analyzer, and smart notifications (for calls, texts, app alerts, etc.) when synced with a compatible smartphone. So, you can stay in touch while staying on top of your game.
